{"title":"水库工地之歌","authors":["许宗尧","朱明道","德崇"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库工地之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠洒地坝修成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠亮晶晶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒遍十三陵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一粒汗珠一颗星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星不如汗珠明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上星星冷清清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的汗珠是热情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠洒地像宝石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠洒地坝修成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许宗尧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众赛过活神仙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三陵前英雄会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲冲破九重天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要让那青山抱绿水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众的智慧赛过活神仙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山腰筑起拦洪坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又浇庄稼又发电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起伏山峦环湖路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃红柳绿景色鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修建剧院迎宾馆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖水之上荡游船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙滩变成好水地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎山变成花果山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非桂林山水到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非西湖在眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫦娥止步不奔月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要来工地把土担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香甜要数劳动果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫过建设祖国的好河山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱明道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扁担挑出幸福来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根扁担软溜溜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑起筐子颤悠悠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给高山大搬家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吱儿啦吱儿啦往前走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在前那个我在后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前后挑起一大溜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左一趟那个右一趟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人来人往似水流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑的那太阳西山落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑的那月亮露了头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑的那大坝往上长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑的那高山低了头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扁担挑出幸福来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑土的人儿乐悠悠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身的劲儿使不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吱儿啦吱儿啦往前走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"德崇"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1}